data.description: Beautiful one-story house, very well kept by the owners, located in the high acclaimed Katy ISD and pretty close to restaurants and stores. High ceilings and a lot of windows allows for tons of natural light. Make an appointment to see this beauty today! THIS HOME IS EQUIPPED WITH SOLAR PANELS THAT WILL KEEP THE ELECTRICITY BILLS VERY LOW BUT THERE IS A BALANCE THAT WOULD NEED TO BE ASSUMED BY THE BUYER.
